<p>Indian Premier League, or IPL, is a cricket league that began in 2008. In more than a decade it has transformed the landscape of cricket not only in India but across the world. This transformation has been achieved by immense amount of money that has been pumped into cricket especially by IPL teams during player auctions.</p>

